Shout out to @CryptoTaxHQ for supporting NFTs in their app.
For ERC721s on proper contracts, it tracks token cost-basis & buy/sell price perfectly.
For ERC1155s and NFTs on shared contracts, it can't quite parse them, but the team is working hard, & keep shipping improvements.
